ng with an "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object. The vector style"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"layer defines the appearance of any content supplied by the shape source. You"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"can update a shape source by setting its "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"shape"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"URL"},{"type":"text","text":" property."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnshapesource"}}}